description: Table showing the number of males and females cautioned, proceeded against at magistrates courts and found guilty at all courts for alcohol related offences, by age group and Government office region (GOR), for the years 2003 to 2007; and the number of persons issued with a penalty notice for disorder (PND) for alcohol related offences for the years 2004 to 2007 by GOR, age group (data are available for persons aged 16 and over) and sex. 5 p.
